title: Govt must show that €1.5bn spend not merely pre-election spree – McGrath (Fianna Fáil)
text: ( Source : Fianna Fáil ) Fianna Fáil Finance spokesperson Michael McGrath has said the government needs to urgently demonstrate that the plan to spend an extra €1.5 billion before the end of the year is not merely a pre-election spending spree
